        "subject": "LU-4139 quota: improve write performance when over softlimit",
        "message": "LU-4139 quota: improve write performance when over softlimit\n\nTo improve the write performance when over softlimit, we choose\nto lose some grace time accuracy: shrinking the qunit size to\n(4 * least_qunit_size) instead of least_qunit_size.\n\nThis patch is back-ported from following patch:\nLustre-commit: e6aae309005b5765ead991af8b8007a8657ba276\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/8078\n\nSigned-off-by: Niu Yawei <yawei.niu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I4996b6bdc85ca523f4891207cbac130f937b8683\n"
